{"id":402,"ayahs":[{"number":46,"arabic":"۞ وَلَا تُجَٰدِلُوٓا۟ أَهْلَ ٱلْكِتَٰبِ إِلَّا بِٱلَّتِى هِىَ أَحْسَنُ إِلَّا ٱلَّذِينَ ظَلَمُوا۟ مِنْهُمْ ۖ وَقُولُوٓا۟ ءَامَنَّا بِٱلَّذِىٓ أُنزِلَ إِلَيْنَا وَأُنزِلَ إِلَيْكُمْ وَإِلَٰهُنَا وَإِلَٰهُكُمْ وَٰحِدٌۭ وَنَحْنُ لَهُۥ مُسْلِمُونَ","translation":"And do not argue with the followers of earlier revelation otherwise than in a most kindly manner - unless it be such of them as are bent on evildoing and say: “We believe in that which has been be­stowed from on high upon us, as well as that which has been bestowed upon you: or our God and your God is one and the same, and it is unto Him that We [all] surrender ourselves.”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3386.mp3","surahId":29,"words":[{"id":46141,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ وَلَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/029_046_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46142,"position":2,"arabic":"تُجَـٰدِلُوٓا۟","translation":"তোমরা বিতর্ক করো","audioUrl":"wbw/029_046_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46143,"position":3,"arabic":"أَهْلَ","translation":"অধিকারীদের","audioUrl":"wbw/029_046_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46144,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْكِتَـٰبِ","translation":"কিতাবের (সাথে)","audioUrl":"wbw/029_046_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46145,"position":5,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এ ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/029_046_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46146,"position":6,"arabic":"بِٱلَّتِى","translation":"দিয়ে তা","audioUrl":"wbw/029_046_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46147,"position":7,"arabic":"هِىَ","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/029_046_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46148,"position":8,"arabic":"أَحْسَنُ","translation":"অতি উত্তম","audioUrl":"wbw/029_046_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46149,"position":9,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"(তবে)ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/029_046_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46150,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"(সেই লোকদের) যারা","aud